parameters: \n<Deorc>"Damn it...! I can't believe this is happening...!"
\n<Riolauno>"Hey, where do you think you're going?"

\n<Riolauno>"...If that's the case, take that woman with you. Someone
will pay for her at least."
\n<Deorc>"Shut up! I'm not dying for money!"

\n<Deorc>"You bastards come too! Don't just leave a woman like that
behind!"
\n<Riolauno>"...Can't be helped. Should I carry her?"
\n<??>"It's okay, relax. I'm on your side."

\n<??>"I know a lot about you. You've been working so hard...
really hard, haven't you?"

\n<??>"I want to support you in your efforts. I want to be your
strength. I want to grant your wishes."
\n<??>"Yes. And for that purpose, I will bestow upon you power."
\n<Ameria>"Haah... haah... Did I do that just now...?"

\n<??>"Yes. That is the power of the path you have wished for,
prayed for, and walked."

\n<The gluttonous grimoire>"Let's respond to your feelings. And let's turn them into
power to illuminate the path you will walk from now on."

\n<The gluttonous grimoire>"Use that power for yourself. For those who need you. Use it
as you wish... good luck."
\n<The gluttonous grimoire>"...Now. Take me in your hands."

Ameria: "I thought having books would save many people. I
believed I could become a great healer."

Ameria: "But that wasn't the case. In the end, I ended up
hurting many people."

Ameria: "This is the sin of not trying to learn properly.
This is the punishment God has given me."

Ameria: "...But. You've been watching over me all this time,
haven't you?"

Ameria: "It was not a falsehood, but my own power that saved
the knight and demon. You have led me this far."
